@startuml
[*] --> Order
state Order
state Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance

Order --> Arrival : plane acquired
Arrival --> Preparation : plane arrived
Preparation --> Operations : plane prepared
Operations --> Maintenance : no more scheduled flights
Maintenance --> Preparation : plane serviced
Preparation --> Operations : plane ready for operations
Operations --> Order : plane no longer available
Order --> Order : plane permanently withdrawn

@enduml
